What is STEM? STEM is a curriculum based on the idea of educating students in science, technology, engineering and mathematics - in an interdisciplinary and applied approach, which is essential for your child’s brighter Why STEM? computing platform and marketplace for computing resources, in the Join our Telegram A Marketplace for Buyers & Sellers Anyone can list and sell computing resources in the Difuon Marketplace and will be connected to those who pay for those Join our Telegram Edge Computing and the Fog The Difuon Network is a worldwide collection of nodes that securely and privately deliver computing resources in the The fog is closer to the data, more efficient, more flexible and less A decentralized fog enables almost anyone to participate in and profit from a compute sharing "Fog computing is a horizontal architecture that distributes resources and services of computing, storage, control and networking anywhere along the It supports multiple industry verticals and application domains, enables services and applications to be distributed closer to the sources, and extends from the things, over the network edges, through the cloud and across multiple protocol " - Open Fog Consortium Problem The Cloud is Centralized Demand for data integration and analytics continues to grow at exponential While the cloud has enabled IT organizations to offload the hassle and expense of proprietary IT infrastructure, the cloud is expensive, generally slower, and it concentrates the value proposition in monolithic siloâd Opportunity Huge Demand and growth Explosive demand growth for data integration and analytics will come from data sourced in the edge (fog): potentially trillions of mobile, IoT, web , and personal cloud devices and Demand for computing infrastructure will data is best processed in the fog at the edge -- not the The fog will displace the cloud as the future home of data integration and analytics Solution Decentralize with the fog Difuon connects buyers and sellers of computing power and associated applications through a decentralized federated ephemeral computing platform and Difuon is beneficially leveraging an unprecedented convergence in technology drivers that will supplant the cloud with Difuonâs Difuon s business model uniquely drives an exponential growth in fog computing Our Software & Platform Difuonâs secret sauce is its holistic, comprehensive artifical intelligence software that federates the entire process in a set it and forget Our remote management capability will enable even the inclined to be fog compute This will foster explosive growth in fog compute capacity as it enables anyone with spare bandwidth, space, and energy to Difuon will take the Cloud to the Fog through: Consensus Engagement Consesus Federation & Remote Difuon brings compute down from the cloud to the fog, infinitely closer to where the data is The rule of data management: Donât move Dedicated Hardware Conventional approaches to decentralized compute erroneously assume that there will be sufficient available spare compute capacity on user s personal laptops, desktops, and mobile This assumption is false because most users will not put up with the inconvenience, security vulnerabilities, and privacy violations that result from running external compute jobs on their personal Difuon addresses these problems by using dedicated hardware that minimizes inconvenience and maximizes security and Our business model incentivizes the deployment of disposable fog compute nodes that monetize spare bandwidth, space, and With remote management these devices require no technical expertise by the user thereby enabling virtually anyone to participate as a Our arrangements with hardware manufacturers enable a scalable delivery model that will foster exponential growth in real compute Security and Privacy Conventional approaches to decentralized compute fail for many One way they fail is by not following best practices for security and Difuon is architected using what we call a diffuse trust perimeterless security model or computing for Difuon uses encryption that is signed and encrypted in motion and at Difuon s ephemeral serverless compute framework runs in a trusted enclove on the dedicated devices thereby providing best practices security and Innovative Tokenomics Model Difuon has designed a novel dual utility tokenomics model consisting of both a (MoE) token and a (SoV) token that together provide true separation of concerns between the need to support stable pricing, low friction, and high throughput transactions and the need for appreciative value to reward virtuous participation on the platform including The new complex SoV token is called a Redemptive Benefit Token (RBT) that employs several complementary features that we call HODLing powers that drives virtuous behavior and value during different growth stages of the This innovative RBT model fixes the broken single utility token
